sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant UI as Advisor surface<br/>(web client)
    participant H as readiness +<br/>behavior hooks
    participant AC as Convex action<br/>requestAdvice
    participant AG as advisor agent<br/>(@convex-dev/agent)
    participant T as agent tools<br/>(catalog, reviews,<br/>recommendations)
    participant LLM as LLM<br/>(via OpenRouter)
    participant V as validation layer
    participant CAT as Convex catalog

    U->>UI: click breathing button or chip
    UI->>H: read aggregated context<br/>(recent products, cart,<br/>favorites, behavior)
    H-->>UI: context payload
    UI->>AC: requestAdvice({ question, context })
    AC->>AG: invoke (model routed<br/>per query type)
    loop tool-calling steps
        AG->>LLM: prompt + tool schemas
        LLM-->>AG: tool calls or final
        AG->>T: execute tool
        T->>CAT: read catalog
        CAT-->>T: rows
        T-->>AG: tool result
    end
    AG-->>AC: { parts, productIds, rationale }
    AC->>V: validate productIds,<br/>strip prices/specs,<br/>check themes
    V-->>AC: cleaned payload
    AC-->>UI: { productIds, rationale }
    UI->>CAT: hydrate productIds<br/>(reactive query)
    CAT-->>UI: live product cards
    UI-->>U: render cards + rationale
